Kendra Moad of Kearns, Utah followed her grandfather out of the house Friday morning and into the driveway . 
  He did not see the toddler and ran her over as he pulled his truck up in the driveway to move the garbage cans . 
  The 20-month-old suffered severe head trauma and was pronounced dead at the hospital . 
  This is the fourth time since August that a child has been run over and killed in their own driveway . 
 